name: Demystification
description: Demystification occurs when you ask and learn about something that used to seem distant, blurry, magical, untouchable. Demystification follows the sense of conquering skills and knowledge, along with a bitter taste that the fairytale is going to end. This the first step towards this goal. Unveiling the myth; to create new ones. It is a debut deliberately leaving many things standing open; presenting paths to be followed, with flaws and obstacles.  .twitter: @aevin_io .instagram: @aevin.io
